OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772719871
OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FThe PSNI has told UTV that it is
OL,7,Finvestigating to establish whether a
OL,8,Fcrime has been committed regarding a
OL,9,Fclub lottery at it's athletic club.
OL,11,FThe issue is said to be of a
OL,12,F"significant financial nature".
OL,14,FAn email was sent to members of the
OL,15,FRUC Athletic Association on Tuesday
OL,16,Fconfirming that the Board had been
OL,17,Falerted to financial matters of
OL,18,Fconcern in February.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
