FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772719871
OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FThis alert was made by the the interim
OL,7,FChief Executive who took office at the
OL,8,Fend of 2025.
OL,10,FAccording to the email seen by UTV,
OL,11,Fthe Chair, Deputy Chief Constable
OL,12,FBobby Singleton, told members that the
OL,13,FBoard has taken immediate steps to
OL,14,Faddress the situation including
OL,15,Fnotifying and engaging with all
OL,16,Frelevant authorities and regulatory
OL,17,Fbodies.
OL,19,FUTV has learned that the PSNI is one
OL,20,Fof those entities which has been
OL,21,Finformed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772719871
OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FWhen UTV contacted the PSNI on
OL,7,FWednesday, they said: "Following a
OL,8,Frecent report from the respective
OL,9,Fboard of trustees, police are
OL,10,Finvestigating to establish whether a
OL,11,Fcrime has been committed regarding a
OL,12,Fclub lottery."
OL,14,FA number of police sources approached
OL,15,Fby UTV would not be drawn on the
OL,16,Fnature of the matters of concern but
OL,17,Fsaid that they are of a "significant
OL,18,Ffinancial nature" and are serious
OL,19,Fenough to warrant the actions taken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
