OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772719871
OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FThe Athletic Association is not a
OL,7,Fstatutory part of the PSNI but is an
OL,8,Findependent charity and non-profit
OL,9,Forganisation.
OL,11,FIt works with PSNI in providing
OL,12,Fsocial, sporting and recreational
OL,13,Fopportunities but is a separate legal
OL,14,Fentity.
OL,16,FMembers have been told that as well as
OL,17,Fthe PSNI investigation, specialist
OL,18,Findependent financial advisors will
OL,19,Fcommence their services immediately.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
