OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FThe RUC Athletic Association was
OL,7,Foriginally established in 1928 to
OL,8,Fpromote sport and recreation for
OL,9,Fmembers of the police force (then the
OL,10,FRoyal Ulster Constabulary).
OL,12,FIt is historically rooted in the
OL,13,Fformer RUC but currently operates in
OL,14,Fassociation with the PSNI sports and
OL,15,Fsocial clubs.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
