OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1772719871
OL,3,CRUC Athletic Association investigated
OL,4,Cover 'significant financial' matters
OL,6,FIt's current core purpose is to
OL,7,Fadvance amateur sport and recreation,
OL,8,Fimprove community engagement and
OL,9,Funderstanding of the police family
OL,10,Fthrough sporting activities and to
OL,11,Fprovide sports facilities, events, and
OL,12,Fresources for use by PSNI members,
OL,13,Ftheir families, and the wider
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
